      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPER MOON (1) finished third (30.20) at this track last time making it four straight placings so far. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the rails draw. Overdue to break through and rates a leading player this line up. JAHREAM (5) stalked the lead after a clean break from the tricky draw and went on to finish second (30.06) at this track in a Maiden over 520m. Expected to feature again. VERDUN (2) settled well back early on debut and boxed on fairly to finish fourth (21.20) at Goulburn over 350m. Can improve sharply here. VOULEZ VROOM (8) is a Barry Riccio-trained newcomer by Fernando Bale out of Rippin' Grace. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can feature with the right run.",
